dct_title_s: National Wetlands Inventory Polygon Portland Metro, Oregon 1998
dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents the National Wetlands Inventory for Portland Metro, Oregon in 1998. The dataset was originally published by the Metro Data Resource Center in February 2001.[This layer is the National Wetland Inventory (NWI) with revisions made by local governments in the tri-county region. These revisions were coordinated by Metro's Growth Management department.]
